When Mr Museveni spoke Saturday night, Mr Kyagulanyi was being held by the army inside his home in Magere, Wakiso District, with no one allowed in or out.
A scheduled press conference with him failed as journalists could not access his home.













Museveni explains why youth voted for him, not Bobi Wine



